										<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2018-01-22T14:09:40+00:00" itemprop="datePublished"><a href="http://www.seobythesea.com/2018/01/google-use-latent-semantic-indexing/#comment-553786" class="comment-time-link" itemprop="url">01/22/2018 at 2:09 pm</a></time></p> </header>
									<div class="comment-content" itemprop="text">
										<p>HI Shamin, </p>
