											<img alt='' src='http://www.seobythesea.com/wp-content/wphb-cache/gravatar/126/1263876229e47a7db8c07c972c782738x60.jpg' srcset='http://www.seobythesea.com/wp-content/wphb-cache/gravatar/126/1263876229e47a7db8c07c972c782738x120.jpg 2x' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60' /><span itemprop="name">Boris</span> <span class="says">says</span> </p>
										<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2018-01-23T01:41:03+00:00" itemprop="datePublished"><a href="http://www.seobythesea.com/2018/01/google-use-latent-semantic-indexing/#comment-553803" class="comment-time-link" itemprop="url">01/23/2018 at 1:41 am</a></time></p> </header>
