										<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2018-02-06T10:37:42+00:00" itemprop="datePublished"><a href="http://www.seobythesea.com/2018/01/google-use-latent-semantic-indexing/#comment-554143" class="comment-time-link" itemprop="url">02/06/2018 at 10:37 am</a></time></p> </header>
